-- Springboks Coach De Villiers Will Face Hearing About Alleged Misconduct
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-07-29T19:54:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/springboks-coach-de-villiers-will-face-hearing-about-alleged-misconduct.html

          
          
             Sanzar said it plans to conduct a
hearing concerning “alleged misconduct” against Springbok
Coach Peter de Villiers following comments he made on
Australia’s Fox Sports “Rugby Club” on July 21.  
 The information was disclosed in an e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        